Google Geo for Research and Higher Education Workshop @ AGU

What: Google Earth for Research and Higher Education Workshop @ AGU
When: December 9, 2013, 4-8:30 PM
Where: Google San Francisco Office, 345 Spear Street (about a 15 minute walk from AGU)
Cost: Attendance is free, following acceptance into the workshop through Google’s application process. A light meal will be provided free to participants.

Please find the complete invitation here:
